== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:1920_Louisiana_hurricane_rainfall_totals.png|thumb]]

路易斯安那州[[摩根城_(路易斯安那州)|摩根城]]至[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(德克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]之间的[[美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区|美国墨西哥湾沿岸地区]]收到[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]<ref name="Coming Up" />，接下来随着气旋逼近，警告范围向东移至[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[彭萨科拉_(佛罗里达州)|彭萨科拉]]至路易斯安那州[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]<ref name="Gulf People">{{cite news | title = Gulf People Flee Before Hurricane | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Washington, D.C. | accessdate = 2016-12-28 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | archivedate = 2016-12-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161228163700/http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482943301&Signature=LmlABX%2FuEk0vKNupqExyLyd4Gr4%3D | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482943301&Signature=LmlABX%2FuEk0vKNupqExyLyd4Gr4%3D | publisher = The New York Times Company | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。可能受到风暴影响的近海区域收到海洋警告<ref name="Coming Up" />，许多船只撤回海岸沿线港口躲避<ref name="Coming Up">{{cite news | title = Great Hurricane Nears Gulf Coast; Coming Up From Yucatan Peninsula | accessdate = 2016-12-28 | newspaper = The Washington Reporter | date = 1920-09-21 | pages = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475,5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119093423/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475%2C5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]的货运列车转移到德克萨斯州大陆，以防万一<ref name="Nears Texas">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Nears Texas Coast | newspaper = The Washington Reporter | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Houston, Texas | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475,5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | pages = 1, 10 | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119093423/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475%2C5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，岛上约有4500居民经城际列车转移<ref name="Inhabitants">{{cite news | title = Ready to Move Inhabitants | newspaper = The Washington Reporter | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Galveston, Texas | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475,5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | pages = 10 | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119093423/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475%2C5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="4,500">{{cite news | title = 4,500 Move Out of Galveston | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482973688&Signature=3ZMby1fwnnkSmW%2FN1uNR6YQvAOE%3D | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Galveston, Texas | publisher = The New York Times Company}}</ref>。[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]接到命令，做好随时应对各类突发紧急状况的准备<ref name="NHC Acts">{{cite news | title = Weather Bureau Acts | newspaper = The Washington Reporter | date = 1920-09-21 | location = Washington, D.C. | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475,5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | pages = 10 | archive-date = 2021-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210119093423/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=30RiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=0XUNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5475%2C5006064&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，正在加尔维斯敦哈钦斯营（{{lang|en|Camp Hutchings}}）执行任务的[[美国国民警卫队|美国国民警卫队]]转移到[[克罗克特堡|克罗克特堡]]（{{lang|en|Fort Crockett}}）的[[营房|营房]]<ref name="Inhabitants" /><ref name="4,500" />。多家[[石油业|石油公司]]在气旋来袭前中止沿海[[油田|油田]]运作<ref name="To Move">{{cite news | title = To Move Residents Off Island | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1920-09-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161229034404/http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482983258&Signature=5gFob8ZahPVHfD%2FILrdhoMz4I4E%3D | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1920/09/22/107002526.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1482983258&Signature=5gFob8ZahPVHfD%2FILrdhoMz4I4E%3D | location = Houston, Texas | archivedate = 2016-12-29 | format = PDF }}</ref>。[[庞恰特雷恩湖|庞恰特雷恩湖]]畔居民转移到新奥尔良，导致酒店暴满，部分人员只能前往包括邮局在内的公共建筑躲避<ref name="Small">{{cite news | title = Small Damage Has Been Done by Hurricane | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XXULAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-FMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1706,3133086&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1920-09-22 | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | page = 10}}</ref>。

墨西哥湾及其北岸出现狂风，船只在风暴增强成飓风前夕测得999毫巴（百帕，29.5英寸汞柱）气压<ref name="Metadata" />。路易斯安那州[[格兰德艾尔_(路易斯安那州)|格兰德艾尔]]测得的持续风速达每小时145公里，向东远至[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]的[[贝圣路易斯_(密西西比州)|贝圣路易斯]]风力时速至少都达到95公里，导致许多树木倒塌，[[高压电线|电缆]]中断<ref name="LA Hurricanes">{{cite book | title = Louisiana Hurricane History | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/lahur.pdf | format = PDF | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | last1 = Roth | first1 = David M | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161221212736/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/lahur.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-12-21 }}</ref>。新奥尔良有一人因电缆断裂触电身亡<ref name="Metadata" />，此外受灾地区的通讯也受到影响，阻碍之后的救灾工作<ref name="Morgan City">{{cite news | title = Morgan City, in Main Path, Not Heard From | location = Washington, D.C. | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1920-09-22 | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XXULAAAAIBAJ&sjid=-FMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1706,3133086&dq=hurricane&hl=en}}</ref>。新奥尔良至少有2500个电话无法使用<ref name="MWR" />，部分房屋的屋顶被狂风刮落<ref name="Small" />。降水主要集中在风暴东半部经过的沿海及内陆地区，大部分降雨都发生在9月21至23日。阿拉巴马州的[[罗伯茨代尔|罗伯茨代尔]]测得300毫米雨量，比其他地点都高<ref name="rainfall">{{cite web | title = Rainfall Associated With Hurricanes (And Other Tropical Disturbances) | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | publisher = United States Weather Bureau's National Hurricane Research Project | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | last1 = Schoner | first1 = R.W. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065316/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | deadurl = no | last2 = Molansky | first2 = S. | page = 63 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF }}</ref>。[[考德威尔堂区_(路易斯安那州)|考德威尔堂区]]的凯利（{{lang|en|Kelly}}）24小时降雨量达到41毫米，刷新9月24小时降雨量纪录<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />。不过，气旋在陆地上空迅速消亡，因此路易斯安那州内陆地区降水普遍不到51毫米。德克萨斯州以[[博蒙特_(得克萨斯州)|博蒙特]]降雨最多，但也只有30毫米。<ref name="MWR" />暴雨令路易斯安那州大范围地区的铁路受到冲刷并遭受破坏，一辆从[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]][[路易维尔_(肯塔基州)|路易维尔]]开往[[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]的列车因铁轨冲蚀严重而被困在庞恰特雷恩湖畔，新奥尔良至阿拉巴马州[[莫比尔_(阿拉巴马州)|莫比尔]]的铁路运输中断<ref name="Sweeps">{{cite news | title = Great Hurricane is Sweeping the Atlantic Coast | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DjdUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TjoNAAAAIBAJ&pg=2737,633684&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-29 | newspaper = Greensburg Daily Tribune | date = 1920-09-22 | location = Galveston, Texas; New Orelans, Louisiana | page = 1 | archive-date = 2020-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201106103913/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DjdUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TjoNAAAAIBAJ&pg=2737%2C633684&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴经过期间，[[博格尼湖|博格尼湖]]（{{lang|en|Lake Borgne}}）和[[密西西比湾|密西西比湾]]（{{lang|en|Mississippi Sound}}）的风暴潮有1.5至1.8米高，密西西比州的[[比洛克西_(密西西比州)|比洛克西]]也测得1.6米的风暴潮<ref name="Metadata" />。强烈的风暴潮对路易斯安那州的格兰德艾尔和马尼拉村（{{lang|en|Manilla Village}}）构成相当严重的破坏<ref name="LA Hurricanes" />。不过飓风来袭时正逢[[潮汐|退潮]]，所以灾情得以减轻。整场风暴共对[[基础设施|基础设施]]构成价值75万美元的破坏，农作物损失总额约为70万美元，其中大部分是水稻和甘蔗<ref name="Metadata" />。
